Fix accessibility issues in the `Modal` component

* Make sure no element outside of the modal can be focused (by any
means, including keyboard and mouse)
* Focus the first keyboard focusable (tabbable) element in the modal
upon opening the modal, or focus the modal itself, if it doesn't
contain any focusable elements
* Focus the element that had focus before the modal was shown upon
closing the modal
* Make sure no element outside of the modal is visible to screen
readers (analog to how we obfuscate the content visually by way of the
backdrop)
* Make sure to transfer focus to the modal only when the modal is
visible, to avoid the document from being scrolled by the browser
